OL,4,C'epidemic', Education Secretary says
OL,6,FEducation Secretary Bridget Phillipson
OL,7,Fhas described the number of children
OL,8,Fmissing school as an "absence
OL,9,Fepidemic".
OL,11,FAhead of pupils' return to the
OL,12,Fclassroom next week, Ms Phillipson
OL,13,Fwarned she will make no "apologies"
OL,14,Ffor fining parents with frequently
OL,15,Fabsent children.
OL,17,FIn the Sunday Times, Ms Phillipson
OL,18,Fsaid her first priority is to create a
OL,19,Fwelcoming environment for pupils in a
OL,20,Fbid to improve attendance.
