OL,6,FThe Commons has previously supported
OL,7,Fthe School Attendance (Duties of Local
OL,8,FAuthorities and Proprietors of
OL,9,FSchools) Bill, which would require
OL,10,Flocal councils in England to promote
OL,11,Fregular attendance and reduce absences
OL,12,Fat schools.
OL,14,FBut the Bill did not reach the House
OL,15,Fof Lords before the general election
OL,16,Fand failed to become law.
